  69,48,"wlw addaea muhamad ealayna shyyana lm nqlh, lantqmna wa'akhadhna minh balymyn, thuma laqataena minh nyat qlbh, fala yuqadar ahd minkum 'ana yhjz eanh eqabna. 'iina hdha alquran lezt lilmutaqin aladhin ymtthlwn 'awamir allah wyjtnbwn nwahyh"
  69,49,"'ina lanelm ann minkm man ykdhdhib bhdha alquran mae wuduh ayath, wa'iin altkdhyb bih lndamt ezymt ealaa alkafirin bih hin yarawn edhabhm wyrwn naeim almuminin bh, wa'iinah lahaqu thabt wyqyn la shaka fyh. fnzzih allah subhanah eamaa la ylyq bjlalh, wadhkrh basmh alezym"
  69,50,"'ina lanelm ann minkm man ykdhdhib bhdha alquran mae wuduh ayath, wa'iin altkdhyb bih lndamt ezymt ealaa alkafirin bih hin yarawn edhabhm wyrwn naeim almuminin bh, wa'iinah lahaqu thabt wyqyn la shaka fyh. fnzzih allah subhanah eamaa la ylyq bjlalh, wadhkrh basmh alezym"
  69,51,"'ina lanelm ann minkm man ykdhdhib bhdha alquran mae wuduh ayath, wa'iin altkdhyb bih lndamt ezymt ealaa alkafirin bih hin yarawn edhabhm wyrwn naeim almuminin bh, wa'iinah lahaqu thabt wyqyn la shaka fyh. fnzzih allah subhanah eamaa la ylyq bjlalh, wadhkrh basmh alezym"
  69,52,"'iinaa lanelm ann minkm man ykdhdhib bhdha alquran mae wuduh ayath, wa'iin altkdhyb bih lndamt ezymt ealaa alkafirin bih hin yarawn edhabhm wyrwn naeim almuminin bh, wa'iinah lahaqu thabt wyqyn la shaka fyh. fnzzih allah subhanah eamaa la ylyq bjlalh, wadhkrh basmh alezym"
  70,1,"dea dae min almushrikin ealaa nafsih waqawmih bnzwl aleadhab elyhm, wahu waqie bihim yawm alqiamat la mhalt, lays lah mane yamnaeah min allah dhi alelw waljlal, tusaeid almalayikat wajibril 'iilayh taealaa fi yawm kan miqdaruh khamsin 'alf sanat min suniyin aldnya, wahu ealaa almumin mithl salat mktwbt"
  70,2,"dea dae min almushrikin ealaa nafsih waqawmih bnzwl aleadhab elyhm, wahu waqie bihim yawm alqiamat la mhalt, lays lah mane yamnaeah min allah dhi alelw waljlal, tusaeid almalayikat wajibril 'iilayh taealaa fi yawm kan miqdaruh khamsin 'alf sanat min suniyin aldnya, wahu ealaa almumin mithl salat mktwbt"
  70,3,"dea dae min almushrikin ealaa nafsih waqawmih bnzwl aleadhab elyhm, wahu waqie bihim yawm alqiamat la mhalt, lays lah mane yamnaeah min allah dhi alelw waljlal, tusaeid almalayikat wajibril 'iilayh taealaa fi yawm kan miqdaruh khamsin 'alf sanat min suniyin aldnya, wahu ealaa almumin mithl salat mktwbt"
  70,4,"dea dae min almushrikin ealaa nafsih waqawmih bnzwl aleadhab elyhm, wahu waqie bihim yawm alqiamat la mhalt, lays lah mane yamnaeah min allah dhi alelw waljlal, tusaeid almalayikat wajibril 'iilayh taealaa fi yawm kan miqdaruh khamsin 'alf sanat min suniyin aldnya, wahu ealaa almumin mithl salat mktwbt"
  70,5,"fasbr -ayha alrswl- ealaa asthzayhm wastejalhm aledhab, sbrana la jze fyh, wala shakwaa minh lighayr allh"
  70,6,"'in alkafirin ystbedwn aleadhab wyrwnh ghyr waqe, wanahn narah waqeana qrybana la mhalt"
  70,7,"'in alkafirin ystbedwn aleadhab wyrwnh ghyr waqe, wanahn narah waqeana qrybana la mhalt"
  70,8,"yawm takun alsama' sayilat mithl huthalt alzyt, watakun aljibal kalswf almsbwgh almanfush aldhy dharath alryh"
  70,9,"ywm takun alsama' sayilat mithl huthalt alzyt, watakun aljibal kalswf almsbwgh almanfush aldhy dharath alryh"
  70,10,wla yas'al qarib qaribuh ean shanh; li'ana kula wahd minhuma mashghul bnfsh